Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七話 冷若寒風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒已經回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校停課了 但令千金的同學還沒回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家雙胞胎的另一個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天起也沒回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們猜測是不是被捲入什麼事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 令千金平安就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過請您轉告她 最近還是不要一個人出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 辛苦你特地跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾 寧寧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能救下她們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從「古物」手中…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 小夜也許辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明約好了要保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和誰約好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保護大家的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親也是 作為這所神社的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到神諭 討伐「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也…定下了約定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能救下眼前的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許能和「古物」戰鬥的巫女只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜 你準備怎麼對付「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會打敗它們的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在兩人決定一同嘗試的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要有這樣的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這個實驗還需要別的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是為了證明雙方觀點哪方正確的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有兩個人是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你準備好了嗎 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 今天聽到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我聽錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我很震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還會有能說話的「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對「古物」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是應該打敗我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我從你身上感覺不到惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡意不是一直放在外面的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能被高明地藏匿起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是「古物」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除「古物」之外亦是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是「古物」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我能感到強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有人為了實現願望而來到店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼店?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以實現願望的店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那家店的看門狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人都是狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有狗來過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 來客各種都有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為能實現願望的店的老闆的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有人許下願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個與我有關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼願望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是怎樣的願望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個現在也不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你確定沒弄錯麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直住在這個鎮上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒出去過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不認識你店裡的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我說 約定好了要保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確約好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒「古物」 保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不起和誰約定了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現願望是需要代價的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且 代價必須與願望相等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以做的很有限
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以這個樣子出現 便是限制之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我約好了會實現這個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且一定會做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 我會在小夜身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間還早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法鎮靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想「這時候 古物不知什麼時候會出現」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它帶去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此 讓它一直在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 小夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 難過的時候不要強顏歡笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天沒吃晚飯就睡了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯芳先生告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在做意式調味飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先吃這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前文人先生說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guimauve的觸感和某個東西很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘴唇…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有意式調味飯不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎雞蛋和熱沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色似乎好些了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為吃過文人先生美味的早餐還有咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 便當和Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午茶的時候吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間還很充裕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為可以在街上慢慢轉轉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天停課
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒通知你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 今天出來得很早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時可能要一直停課了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 即便是找到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕也會很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前跟你說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃人的東西的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求衛諾諾和寧寧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定已經被那個東西給吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直失蹤到現在的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計也一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 你也這麼想吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 頭又痛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就回去吧 回到你父親那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒鳥老師為什麼突然說那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於「古物」似乎知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去學校?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天應該停課的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 通知來之前就從家裡出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在雖說還很早 可要是發生什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真窩囊 居然變得如此地弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些被打敗的傢伙一樣窩囊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的你暫且不論
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被這種水準的人消滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算活了下來 也只有恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有和你打呢 憑什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱 太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我母親戰鬥過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這把神刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和母親相比 我或許弱了些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我一定要把你們「古物」打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父親 唯芳是這麼說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個神社裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺著一幅玄乎的臉 給你一把神刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑毛!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能忍住笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯芳居然讓你來打敗我們?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和唯芳都太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這不正是白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親才不愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他堅強而又溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從母親去世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直在支持著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在講什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你 你究竟在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是想迷惑我的鬼話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡言亂語的是人類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用胡言亂語和謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷地違反著約定的 是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趁早給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 把唯芳也滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 能和思慕的父親一同被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你的心願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓你到父親那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是這感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那時的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好去問問唯芳 你的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時真…同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和誰約定要打倒古物的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要實現願望的 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽扯進來的話會很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就更想知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你對於我是很特別的 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.02,0:23:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 Blood-C
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生在世







